<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1004,1498]" pageId="1" pageNumber="532">
The Palaearctic species of the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Becker" authorityYear="1894" box="[582,722,1005,1031]" class="Insecta" family="Scathophagidae" genus="Acerocnema" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="532" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[582,722,1005,1031]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="532">Acerocnema</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were revised and defined by 
<bibRefCitation author="Ozerov, A. L." box="[1070,1230,1004,1031]" pageId="1" pageNumber="532" pagination="333 - 336" refId="ref12697" refString="Ozerov, A. L. (2006) New species of the family Scathophagidae (Diptera) from Altai and Far East of Russia. Euroasian Entomological Journal, 5, 333 - 336. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="2006">Ozerov (2006</bibRefCitation>
, 2014) and 
<bibRefCitation author="Iwasa, M." pageId="1" pageNumber="532" pagination="175 - 183" refId="ref12300" refString="Iwasa, M. (2014) Three new species of the genus Acerocnema Becker (Diptera: Scathophagidae) from Japan, with a key to the Palaearctic species. Studia dipterologica, 20, 175 - 183. [2013]" type="journal article" year="2014">Iwasa (2014)</bibRefCitation>
. The Nearctic fauna was recently revised by 
<bibRefCitation author="Chagnon, M. - E. &amp; Sinclair, B. J." box="[732,1041,1040,1067]" pageId="1" pageNumber="532" pagination="369 - 403" refId="ref11716" refString="Chagnon, M. - E. &amp; Sinclair, B. J. (2020) Revision of the Nearctic species of Gimnomera Rondani (Diptera: Scathophagidae), with morphological phylogeny and DNA barcodes. Zootaxa, 4853 (3), 369 - 403. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4853.3.3" type="journal article" year="2020">Chagnon &amp; Sinclair (2020)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
